==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Silesia
<hw>Si*le"si*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A kind
of linen cloth, originally made in <xex>Silesia</xex>, a province of
Prussia.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A twilled cotton fabric, used for dress
linings.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Silesian</ent>⟦br⟧
